  "text": "All of data were collected from the Thrombolysis Implementation and Monitor of acute ischemic Stroke in China (TIMS-China) registry [CITATION_1] , a national prospective stroke registry of thrombolytic therapy with intravenous alteplase in patients with acute ischemic stroke in China. In nationwide, 67 centers participated in this stroke registry between May 2007 and April 2012. Demographics on clinical characteristics, cranial CT scans, medical therapy and thrombolysis information were collected. All patients were followed up for 3 months.",
